articles.author: By Forrest Brown, CNN
articles.title: CDC moves large European country to its highest level of Covid-19 travel risk - CNN
articles.description: The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention has added just one new destination to its list of "very high" risk travel destinations. Ukraine, Europe's second-largest country by area, is moved to Level 4.
